ave%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Ray%20spent%20years%20waiting%20tables%20and%20bartending%20to%20pay%20his%20bills%20while%20building%20a%20window%20cleaning%20business%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20about%20seven%20years%20after%20landing%20his%20first%20client%20%E2%80%94%20a%20massage%20parlor%20in%20a%20strip%20mall%20in%20Houston%20%E2%80%94%20he%20started%20earning%20enough%20income%20from%20his%20side%20gig%2C%20which%20he%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgeekwindowcleaning.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeek%20Window%20Cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20quit%20his%20service%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference-maker%20was%20SEO.%20Around%202013%2C%20he%20started%20paying%20attention%20to%20search%20engine%20optimization%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20leverage%20it%20to%20boost%20traffic%20to%20his%20site.%20By%202015%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20were%20Googling%20'window%20cleaning%20Houston%2C'%20we%20were%20showing%20up%20in%20the%20No.%201%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20entrepreneur%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThen%20we%20started%20getting%20really%20busy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20the%20strategy%20that%20helped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbartender-turned-window-cleaning-side-hustle-into-six-figure-business-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransform%20Ray's%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20side%20hustle%20to%20a%20full-time%20gig%20is%20essentially%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20fired%20the%20SEO%20company%20that%20we%20used%20to%20use.%20I%20no%20longer%20care%20about%20ranking%20on%20Google.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20because%20search%20is%20going%20to%20a%20zero%20click%20so%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20Google%20something%2C%20Gemini%20tells%20you%20whatever%20the%20answer%20is%20right%20there.%20You%20don't%20even%20scroll%20down%20the%20page%20to%20see%20what's%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20has%20progressed%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20Ray%20has%20committed%20to%20mastering%20it%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20he%20tackled%20SEO%20in%20the%20early%202010s.%20He's%20already%20seeing%20results%3A%20Having%20generated%20six%20figures%20in%20revenue%20in%202024%2C%20he's%20on%20track%20to%20exceed%20%241%20million%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20his%20ServiceMonster%20dashboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20software%20and%20AI%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20when%20it%20makes%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20tech%20stack%20is%20kind%20of%20wild.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20rattled%20off%20a%20handful%20of%20AI%20and%20software%20tools%20that%20he%20uses%20to%20save%20time%20and%20money%20as%20a%20small-business%20owner%20%E2%80%94%20Usewhale.io%2C%20ChatGPT%2C%20Ingage%2C%20Canva%2C%20Calendly%2C%20PriceGuide.ai%2C%20Chiirp%2C%20Paive%2C%20ServiceMonster%2C%20ZyraTalk%2C%20ClickUp%2C%20and%20MindMeister%20%E2%80%94%20and%20highlighted%20the%20ones%20that%20he%20uses%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kyle%20ray%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cd8dd0f9db348adc0bd3df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKyle%20Ray%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Geek%20Window%20Cleaning.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kyle%20Ray%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EServiceMonster%20to%20manage%20customers.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERay%20said%20that%20shifting%20to%20a%20CRM%20(customer%20relationship%20management)%20software%20has%20progressed%20his%20business%20more%20than%20any%20other%20tool%2C%20and%20helped%20him%20stay%20organized%20as%20he's%20expanded%20to%20servicing%20hundreds%20of%20clients%20throughout%20Houston%20and%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20he%20used%20carbon%20copy%20paper%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20his%20customer%20history%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20in%20a%20folder%20and%20you're%20always%20like%2C%20'What%20happens%20if%20my%20office%20catches%20fire%20and%20I%20lose%20all%20this%20data%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20using%20ServiceMonster%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can%20pull%20up%20your%20account%20history%2C%20what%20we%20did%2C%20and%20what%20notes%20are%20on%20your%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20includes%20notes%20of%20even%20the%20smallest%20details%2C%20such%20as%20the%20name%20of%20a%20client's%20pet%2C%20to%20provide%20his%20clients%20with%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bunreasonable%20hospitality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChatGPT%20for%20just%20about%20everything.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERay%20said%20he%20uses%20ChatGPT%20every%20day%20to%20do%20anything%20from%20feeding%20it%20Geek's%20P%26amp%3BL%20and%20asking%20how%20he%20can%20expand%20margins%20to%20asking%20what%20new%20AI%20tools%20he%20should%20be%20using%20as%20a%20business%20owner%20in%20the%20home%20services%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20he%20feels%20as%20if%20he%20has%20access%20to%20a%20leadership%20team%20without%20having%20to%20hire%20anyone%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20me.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20CFO%20or%20a%20CEO%20or%20a%20COO%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20wearing%20all%20those%20hats%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20can%20create%20ones%20in%20ChatGPT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20uses%20his%20%26quot%3BAI%20CFO%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BAI%20COO%26quot%3B%20for%20basic%20questions%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20something%20really%20complicated%20or%20something%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20or%20look%20at%2C%20I%20have%20a%20friend%20who's%20the%20CFO%20for%20a%20massive%20company%2C%20and%20I%20can%20call%20him.%20His%20experience%20is%20going%20to%20be%20better%20than%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChiirp%20and%20ZyraTalk%20for%20customer%20communication.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20our%20phone%20to%20always%20be%20answered.%20I%20don't%20ever%20want%20it%20to%20go%20to%20voicemail%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ray%2C%20who%20uses%20AI%20to%20handle%20calls%20that%20come%20in%20after%20hours%20or%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChiirp%2C%20a%20texting%20software%2C%20can%20handle%20basic%20conversations%20with%20customers%2C%20while%20ZyraTalk%20is%20an%20AI%20voice%20assistant%20that%20answers%20missed%20phone%20calls%20and%20speaks%20to%20customers%20like%20your%20team%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20training%20these%20two%20AI%20tools%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20need%20to%20have%20a%20full%20team%20of%20customer%20service%20reps%2C%26quot%3B%20Ray%20said.%20%26quot%3BSmaller%20businesses%20like%20mine%2C%20it's%20hard%20%E2%80%94%20I%20can't%20scale%20at%20that%20speed%20or%20hire%20that%20fast%20and%20train%2C%20but%20I%20can%20train%20an%20AI%20voice%20bot%20to%20answer%20the%20phones%20when%20people%20are%20calling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPriceGuide.ai%20and%20Calendly%20for%20creating%20a%20frictionless%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ray%20wants%20prospective%20customers%20to%20book%20window%20cleanings%20as%20seamlessly%20as%20possible.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20uses%20PriceGuide.ai%2C%20which%20helps%20service-based%20businesses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.priceguide.ai%2Festimator%2FrecDPhFtkX8zonqrQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20pricing%20estimators%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20streamline%20the%20early-quote%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20new%20client%20receives%20their%20estimate%2C%20they%20can%20book%20their%20initial%20cleaning%20through%20the%20scheduling%20platform%20Calendly%2C%20meaning%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20can%20go%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20without%20talking%20to%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERay%20said%20he's%20constantly%20testing%20different%20software%20tools%20to%20determine%20what%20works%20best%20for%20him%20and%20Geek.%20He%20believes%20that%20every%20entrepreneur%20should%20con