t%20surpasses%20human%20capability%E2%80%94%20be%20achieved%20in%20the%20very%20near%20future%2C%20but%20that%20soon%20there%20could%20be%20breakthroughs%20that%20will%20only%20be%20achievable%20through%20the%20use%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20and%20candid%20interview%20that%20covered%20everything%20from%20how%20Altman%20thinks%20his%20own%20child%20will%20interact%20with%20the%20technology%20to%20what%20he%20doesn't%20use%20ChatGPT%20for%2C%20Altman%20was%20perhaps%20unsurprisingly%20optimistic%20about%20the%20ability%20to%20align%20the%20technology%20with%20human%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20gave%20a%20glimpse%20into%20OpenAI's%20hardware%20ambitions%2C%20hinting%20at%20an%20eventual%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20of%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20other%20musings%20about%20an%20AI%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWELT%20Editor-in-Chief%20Jan%20Philipp%20Burgard%20interviewed%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%20this%20week%20in%20Berlin%2C%20where%20Altman%20received%20this%20year's%20Axel%20Springer%20Award.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20Q%26amp%3BA%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWelt%3A%20Sam%2C%20what%20quality%20of%20yours%20will%20artificial%20intelligence%20never%20be%20able%20to%20replace%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%3A%20I%20guess%20we'll%20find%20out.%20But%2C%20something%20that%20is%20really%20unique%20is%20how%20much%20people%20care%20about%20other%20people%20and%20what%20they%20do%2C%20how%20much%20people%20want%20to%20interact%20with%20other%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20these%20qualities%20will%20be%20increasingly%20important%20in%20the%20world%20of%20AI.%20We'll%20have%20an%20incredible%20tool%20at%20our%20disposal%2C%20but%20we%20still%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%2C%20what%20other%20people%20want%2C%20and%20what%20other%20people%20will%20find%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20developing%20rapidly.%20When%20exactly%20do%20you%20think%20there%20will%20be%20a%20superintelligence%20that%20is%20smarter%20than%20humans%20in%20all%20aspects%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20GPT5%20is%20already%20smarter%20than%20me%2C%20at%20least%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20people%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPT5%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20incredible%20things%20that%20many%20people%20find%20very%20impressive.%20But%20it's%20also%20not%20able%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20humans%20could%20do%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20will%20be%20the%20case%20for%20a%20while%2C%20as%20humans%20use%20these%20tools%20and%20apply%20their%20human%20insight%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20ingenuity%20in%20really%20important%20ways.%20I%20expect%2C%20though%2C%20the%20trajectory%20of%20AI's%20capability%20progress%20to%20remain%20extremely%20steep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20the%20three%20years%20since%20ChatGPT%20launched%2C%20the%20models%20have%20become%20much%20more%20capable.%20And%20I%20see%20no%20sign%20of%20that%20slowing%20down.%20In%20another%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20it%20will%20become%20very%20plausible%20for%20AI%20to%20make%2C%20for%20example%2C%20scientific%20discoveries%20that%20humans%20cannot%20make%20on%20their%20own.%20To%20me%2C%20that'll%20start%20to%20feel%20like%20something%20we%20could%20properly%20call%20superintelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20an%20exact%20year%20in%20which%20you%20expect%20this%20superintelligence%20to%20emerge%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20certainly%20say%20that%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade%2C%20by%202030%2C%20if%20we%20don't%20have%20extraordinarily%20capable%20models%20that%20do%20things%20that%20we%20ourselves%20cannot%20do%2C%20I'd%20be%20very%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20if%20in%202026%20we%20don't%20see%20a%20similar%20rate%20of%20progress%20we've%20seen%20in%202024%20and%202025%2C%20I'd%20also%20be%20surprised.%20That%20means%20that%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20I%20would%20expect%20models%20that%2C%20if%20we%20had%20them%20today%2C%20would%20be%20quite%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20percentage%20of%20today's%20jobs%20could%20disappear%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20the%20jobs%20that%20we%20did%2030%20years%20ago%20that%20may%20not%20exist%20at%20all%20today%2C%20or%20new%20jobs%20that%20were%20difficult%20to%20imagine%2030%20years%20ago%20that%20are%20now%20commonplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20a%20statistic%20that%20about%20half%20the%20jobs%20in%20society%20change%20over%20every%2075%20years.%20That's%20even%20without%20AI.%20It%20may%20happen%2C%20and%20I%20expect%20it%20will%20happen%20faster%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20it%20useful%20to%20think%20about%20tasks%2C%20not%20the%20percentage%20of%20jobs.%20There%20will%20be%20many%20jobs%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20do%20that%20job%20changes.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20will%20be%20totally%20new%20jobs.%20And%20many%20existing%20jobs%20will%20disappear%20entirely%20and%20be%20replaced%20by%20these%20new%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20more%20interesting%20thing%20is%2C%20of%20everyone's%20jobs%2C%20what%20percentage%20of%20the%20tasks%20you%20do%20every%20day%20will%20be%20done%20by%20AI%3F%20I%20can%20easily%20imagine%20a%20world%20where%2030%20to%2040%25%20of%20the%20tasks%20that%20happen%20in%20the%20economy%20today%20get%20done%20by%20AI%20in%20the%20not%20very%20distant%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20became%20a%20father%20this%20year.%20What%20education%20would%20you%20advise%20your%20son%20to%20pursue%20so%20that%20his%20job%20won't%20simply%20be%20replaced%20by%20AI%20in%2030%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meta-skill%20of%20learning%20how%20to%20learn%2C%20of%20learning%20to%20adapt%2C%20learning%20to%20be%20resilient%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20change.%20I%20mentioned%20this%20earlier%2C%20but%20learning%20how%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20people%20want%2C%20how%20to%20make%20useful%20products%20and%20services%20for%20them%2C%20and%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20confident%20that%20people%20will%20still%20be%20the%20center%20of%20the%20story%20for%20each%20other.%20Anything%20in%20that%20world%20will%20be%20great.%20I'm%20also%20confident%20that%20human%20desire%20for%20new%20stuff%2C%20desire%20to%20be%20useful%20to%20other%20people%2C%20and%20desire%20to%20express%20our%20creativity%20are%20all%20limitless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20rightly%20wonder%2C%20in%20all%20these%20previous%20technological%20revolutions%2C%20what%20we%20are%20all%20going%20to%20do.%20In%20the%20industrial%20age%2C%20these%20machines%20came%20along.%20We%20watched%20them%20do%20the%20things%20that%20we%20used%20to%20do%20and%20said%2C%20'What%20would%20be%20our%20role%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20new%20generation%20uses%20its%20creativity%2C%20new%20ideas%2C%20and%20all%20of%20the%20tools%20the%20previous%20generation%20built%20for%20them%20to%20astonish%20us.%20I'm%20sure%20my%20kids%20will%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20sound%20very%20optimistic%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20AI%20critics.%20For%20example%2C%20researcher%20Eliezer%20Yudkowsky%20says%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20superintelligence%20and%20humans%20is%20roughly%20the%20same%20as%20the%20relationship%20between%20humans%20and%20ants.%20Do%20you%20fear%20that%20AI%20will%20eventually%20view%20us%20as%20ants%20and%20simply%20destroy%20us%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20heard%20many%20people%20describe%20many%20different%20ways%20of%20envisioning%20the%20relationship%20between%20AI%20and%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20has%20always%20been%20my%20favorite%20is%20my%20cofounder%2C%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20who%20once%20said%20that%20he%20hoped%20that%20the%20way%20that%20an%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20would%20treat%20humanity%2C%20or%20all%20AGIs%20would%20treat%20humanity%2C%20is%20like%20a%20loving%20parent.%20When%20we%20ask%20that%20question%2C%20we%20are%20sort%20of%20anthropomorphizing%20AGI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20this%20tool%20will%20be%20enormously%20capable.%20Even%20if%20it%20has%20no%20intentionality%2C%20asking%20it%20to%20do%20something%20could%20have%20consequences%20we%20don't%20understand.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20very%20important%20that%20we%20align%20it%20with%20human%20values.%20I%20don't%20think%20it'll%20treat%20humans%20like%20ants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECritics%20accuse%20you%20of%20transforming%20OpenAI%20from%20a%20nonprofit%20institution%20into%20a%20commercial%20enterprise%20and%20of%20partially%20disregarding%20the%20security%20risks%20in%20the%20process.%20Do%20you%20agree%20with%20this%20criticism%3F%20Or%2C%20do%20you%20think%20that%20sometimes%20you%20just%20have%20to%20forge%20ahead%20to%20make%20progress%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20we%20still%20have%20a%20nonprofit%20entity%2C%20and%20we%20always%20will.%20I%20hope%20that%20we%20will%20have%20the%20best-resourced%20and%20hopefully%20the%20most%20impactful%20nonprofit%20of%20all%20time.%20This%20is%20very%20important%20to%20our%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20governance%20role%20of%20this%20is%20also%20important%20to%20our%20mission%2C%20as%20is%20ensuring%20that%20we%20stick%20to%20our%20mission%20and%20prioritize%20safety%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20the%20maximum%20benefit%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20obviously%20made%20some%20mistakes%2C%20as%20we%20understand%20that%20with%20this%20new%20technology%2C%20we'll%20make%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20overall%2C%20I'm%20extremely%20proud%20of%20our%20team's%20track%20record%20on%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20these%20services%20safe%2C%20broadly%20beneficial%2C%20and%20widely%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20our%20core%20beliefs%20is%20that%20if%20we%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20build%20this%20tool%2C%20align%20it%20with%20human%20values%2C%20and%20then%20put%20it%20out%20into%20people's%20hands%20and%20have%20them%20express%20all%20of%20the%20things%20they%20want%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20that%20will%20be%20great%20for%20the%20world%20and%20is%20deeply%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20world%20is%20watching%20OpenAI's%20hardware%20innovation.%20You%20hired%20an%20Apple%20designer%20for%20this.%20We%20can%20assume%20the%20device%20will%20look%20good%2C%20but%20what%20will%20it%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20good-looking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20big%20revolutions%20in%20computer%20use%20have%20occurred%3A%20the%20mouse%20and%20keyboard%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20monitor%20displaying%20this%20sort%20of%20windowed%20system.%20That%20was%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20for%20sure.%20Then%20we%20had%20the%20touch%20devices%2C%20which%20adapted%20that%2C%20taking%20out%20the%20mouse%20and%20letting%20you%20use%20your%20finger%2C%20making%20it%20a%20very%20personal%20device.%20This%20was%20huge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFundamentally%2C%20we%20have%20never%20had%20something%20as%20powerful%20as%20AI.%20Computers%20really%20can%20understand%20what%20we%20want%2C%20can%20think%2C%20which%20has%20let%20us%20reimagine%20what%20it%20could%20mean%20to%20use%20a%20computer.%20So%20we're%20still%20exploring.%20It'll%20take%20us%20quite%20some%20time.%20Don't%20expect%20anything%20very%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20I%20expect%20we'll%20make%20a%20small%20family%20of%20devices.%20They%20will%20look%20good%2C%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20main%20thing.%20I%20hope%20that%20if%20we%20do%20a%20really%20great%20job%2C%20they%20will%20change%20what%20it%20means%20to%20use%20a%20computer%2C%20how%20you%20do%20your%20work%2C%20and%20how%20you%20play%20and%20live%20your%20life.%20But%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20and%20a%20lot%20to%20explore%20between%20here%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20give%20me%20an%20example%20of%20one%20feature%20or%20capability%20that%20such%20a%20device%20could%20have%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20do%20a%20task%20on%20a%20computer%2C%20you%20have%20to%20click%20around%20and%20go%20between%20a%20bunch%20of%20applications.%20If%20it's%20a%20difficult%20task%2C%20it%20might%20take%20you%20a%20while.%20One%20of%20the%20promises%20of%20AI%20is%20that%20you%20can%20say%20something%20complex%20that%20needs%20to%20happen%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20day%2C%20a%20month%2C%20or%20even%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20just%20trust%20that%20the%20computer%20will%20understand%20it%2C%20do%20it%20for%20you%2C%20and%20come%20back%20to%20you%20when%20it%20needs%20help.%20But%20you%20can%20imagine%20asking%20a%20computer%20a%20very%20nuanced%2C%20complex%2C%20but%20brief%20question%20and%20then%20just%20trusting%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20and%20come%20back%20to%20you%20when%20it%20needs%20help.%20That%20would%20totally%20change%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20use%20the%20computer%20instead%20of%20launching%20a%20bunch%20of%20apps%20and%20having%20notifications%20constantly%20come%20up.%20So%20that's%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20US%20tech%20industry%20has%20long%20had%20a%20liberal-democratic%20tone.%20Now%2C%20many%20tech%20leaders%20are%20showing%20their%20support%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20How%20do%20you%20explain%20this%20vibe%20shift%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20industry%20should%20work%20with%20whoever%20the%20American%20president%20is.%20But%20in%20this%20specific%20case%2C%20I%20think%20there%20have%20been%20some%20welcome%20policy%20changes.%20The%20ability%20to%20build%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20US%20has%20been%20quite%20difficult%20and%20quite%20important%20to%20companies%20like%20ours.%20President%20Trump%20has%20done%20an%20amazing%20job%20of%20supporting%20this.%20A%20generally%20more%20pro-business%20and%20pro-tech%20climate%20has%20also%20been%20a%20welcome%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20US%20is%20very%20polarized%2C%20downright%20divided.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20simply%20letting%20AI%20govern%20instead%20of%20a%20US%20president%20in%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20people%20want%20that%20anytime%20soon.%20What%20I%20expect%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20presidents%20and%20leaders%20around%20the%20world%20will%20use%20AI%20more%20and%20more%20to%20help%20them%20with%20complex%20decisions.%20But%20I%20think%20we%20all%20still%20want%20a%20human%2C%20signing%20off%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20finish%20up%2C%20many%20people%20are%20getting%20relationship%20advice%20from%20ChatGPT.%20Have%20you%20ever%20asked%20your%20own%20bot%20for%20help%20with%20relationship%20issues%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20use%20it%20as%20much%20for%20that%20as%20other%20people%20do.%20I've%20tried%20it%2C%20but%20no%2C%20that's%20not%20one%20of%20my%20big%20personal%20use%20cases.%20But%20it's%20clearly%20something%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20use%20it%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-predicts-ai-agi-surpass-human-intelligence-2030-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758877202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d5c7a2cc993f9955cef52b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-predicts-ai-agi-surpass-human-intelligence-2030-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20expects%20AI%20will%20exceed%20human%20intelligence%20by%202030.%20He%20emphasized%20AI's%20potential%20in%20scientific%20breakthroughs%20and%20novel%20uses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22inside